<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-style>.mjbody a, .mjbody a:hover, .mjbody a:active, .mjbody a[href], .mjbody a[href]:hover, .mjbody a[href]:active {color: inherit;text-decoration: underline}</mj-style>
    <mj-breakpoint width="480px" />
    <mj-font name="Benton Sans" href="https://www.masters.com/assets/fonts/bentonsans/BentonSans-Book.woff2" />
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body width="660px" background-color="#EEEEEE" css-class="mjbody">
    <mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" background-color="#EEEEEE"><mj-column width="50%"><mj-text color="#333333" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="12px" line-height="19px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px">Your Daily Briefing from Augusta National</mj-text></mj-column><mj-column width="50%"><mj-text align="right" color="#006744" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="12px" line-height="19px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px"><span><a href="#">View in browser</a></span></mj-text></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/j7pqm2yl_welcomeback.jpg" alt="Welcome Back" width="660px" href="https://www.masters.com"></mj-image></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-text color="#25282A" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px">So begins a week full of anticipation. Players arrive with high hopes and Green Jacket dreams. By Sunday, someone's name will be etched into Masters history. But before glory can be claimed, there's work to be done. Welcome to the 90th Masters Tournament.</mj-text></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="10px" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="10px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-text color="#006744" font-family="tiempos-light, Georgia, sans-serif" font-size="24px" line-height="31px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" font-weight="normal">Featured</mj-text></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/catwh95i_1540584_mondaytrailer-040626.png" alt="Monday at the Masters" width="290px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIObX6A0o_JfwFQbrD2cCHufvhdN341Sihz_flN752ZXQKOk6mlHkJbGi"></mj-image></mj-column><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-text color="#006744" font-family="tiempos-light, Georgia, sans-serif" font-size="20px" line-height="31px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="5px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="10px"><span><a href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIObX6A0o_JfwFQbrD2cCHufvhdN341Sihz_flN752ZXQKOk6mlHkJbGi">Monday at the Masters</a></span></mj-text><mj-text color="#25282A" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px">Today is the day we've been waiting for. Welcome back to this annual rite of spring. It is, at long last, Monday at the Masters.</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#F7DF01" border-radius="0px" color="#006744" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" letter-spacing="1px" line-height="20px" inner-padding="8px 10px 8px 10px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIObX6A0o_JfwFQbrD2cCHufvhdN341Sihz_flN752ZXQKOk6mlHkJbGi">WATCH TRAILER</mj-button></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-divider border-width="2px" border-color="#EEEEEE" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px"></mj-divider></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/5o1ivylt_1540567_rangetracker-040626.png" alt="Range Tracker" width="290px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBINnF6A0o_JfwFYVaJji445OUYK_2B02Bk7yz9TNKNrSDAO7l0zB_J7gy"></mj-image></mj-column><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-text color="#006744" font-family="tiempos-light, Georgia, sans-serif" font-size="20px" line-height="31px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="5px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="10px"><span><a href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBINnF6A0o_JfwFYVaJji445OUYK_2B02Bk7yz9TNKNrSDAO7l0zB_J7gy">Range Tracker</a></span></mj-text><mj-text color="#25282A" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px">Follow every shot from the Tournament Practice Area today as players fine-tune their game for the week ahead.</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#F7DF01" border-radius="0px" color="#006744" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" letter-spacing="1px" line-height="20px" inner-padding="8px 14px 8px 14px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBINnF6A0o_JfwFYVaJji445OUYK_2B02Bk7yz9TNKNrSDAO7l0zB_J7gy">VIEW TRACKER</mj-button></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-divider border-width="2px" border-color="#EEEEEE" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px"></mj-divider></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/ef1rh4lg_1540575_earlyarrivals-040526.png" alt="A Sunday Stroll" width="290px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIPLH6A0o_JfwFaqJfoCWEFN_0IBqY-Ma888CuxrqtMctE4eMRQY0uy0n"></mj-image></mj-column><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-text color="#006744" font-family="tiempos-light, Georgia, sans-serif" font-size="20px" line-height="31px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="5px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="10px"><span><a href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIPLH6A0o_JfwFaqJfoCWEFN_0IBqY-Ma888CuxrqtMctE4eMRQY0uy0n">A Sunday Stroll</a></span></mj-text><mj-text color="#25282A" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px">After the Drive, Chip and Putt National Finals, many of the game's biggest names got in some early work at Augusta National.</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#F7DF01" border-radius="0px" color="#006744" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" letter-spacing="1px" line-height="20px" inner-padding="8px 15px 8px 15px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIPLH6A0o_JfwFaqJfoCWEFN_0IBqY-Ma888CuxrqtMctE4eMRQY0uy0n">VIEW GALLERY</mj-button></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-divider border-width="2px" border-color="#EEEEEE" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px"></mj-divider></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/w2ljdtgo_1540582_playingthepatch-040526.png" alt="Playing The Patch" width="290px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIJDN6A0o_JfwFepenZCPWQXNoge9eZJZfdMVyJVCeDdeeyRlZDfGokOi"></mj-image></mj-column><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-text color="#006744" font-family="tiempos-light, Georgia, sans-serif" font-size="20px" line-height="31px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="5px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="10px"><span><a href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIJDN6A0o_JfwFepenZCPWQXNoge9eZJZfdMVyJVCeDdeeyRlZDfGokOi">Playing The Patch</a></span></mj-text><mj-text color="#25282A" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px">For nearly a century, Augusta Municipal Golf Course – more affectionately known as The Patch – has been an institution. It opens to the public once again on April 15.</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#F7DF01" border-radius="0px" color="#006744" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" letter-spacing="1px" line-height="20px" inner-padding="8px 15px 8px 15px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIJDN6A0o_JfwFepenZCPWQXNoge9eZJZfdMVyJVCeDdeeyRlZDfGokOi">READ ARTICLE</mj-button></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-divider border-width="2px" border-color="#EEEEEE" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px"></mj-divider></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/6twsaofq_1540581_purehappiness-040526.png" alt="Pure Happiness on Display" width="290px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBILbJ6A0o_JfwFWY9AIcC_KBx2cyDvVTODtjQBrYVnMHsjczaGcdgmJJL"></mj-image></mj-column><mj-column padding-bottom="10px" width="50%"><mj-text color="#006744" font-family="tiempos-light, Georgia, sans-serif" font-size="20px" line-height="31px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="5px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="10px"><span><a href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBILbJ6A0o_JfwFWY9AIcC_KBx2cyDvVTODtjQBrYVnMHsjczaGcdgmJJL">Pure Happiness on Display</a></span></mj-text><mj-text color="#25282A" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px">Each year, the participants in the Drive, Chip and Putt National Finals remind us what pure happiness looks like.</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#F7DF01" border-radius="0px" color="#006744" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="bold" letter-spacing="1px" line-height="20px" inner-padding="8px 16px 8px 16px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBILbJ6A0o_JfwFWY9AIcC_KBx2cyDvVTODtjQBrYVnMHsjczaGcdgmJJL">WATCH RECAP</mj-button></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-spacer height="10px" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" padding-right="0px"></mj-spacer></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="25px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="10px" padding-left="10px" background-color="#1C4932"><mj-column><mj-social border-radius="0px" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" icon-size="24px" mode="horizontal" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px"><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIObB6A0o_JfwFSId-NXxXDkZxlBL87gwq0BSDQ0ubgW92y7Z8ZMisBh7" alt="Facebook" background-color="#3b5998" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/cxhzkclel5ojn_dzo1o7v_facebook.png"></mj-social-element><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="8px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIOfB6A0o_JfwFU9-dsx38lJp8ArLXQ89m1RwH4aGVAx8lbkplbhlsH3M" alt="Instagram" background-color="#3f729b" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/yyeuinjdwnclhwonzm04p_instagram.png"></mj-social-element><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="8px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIOnB6A0o_JfwFXpot2lxf9o9lFxXxQK-NKEIvtUW_AD4LyF9l0Ld3VLB" alt="Twitter" background-color="#000000" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/vjjjm0-8wv5-oumveqyna_twitter-x.png"></mj-social-element><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="8px" href="https://email.masters.com/c/AQjHkhMQ5ck3GPLlyMYBIOrB6A0o_JfwFcVizRj5CxEtkz5qkTZP1s_TwUvNRFIwRgn8aLktBq7T" alt="YouTube" background-color="#EB3323" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/j5wv-vgx4tse62wzjde4q_youtube.png"></mj-social-element></mj-social></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="10px" background-color="#1C4932"><mj-column><mj-text align="center" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="12px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px">Copyright © 2026 The Masters, All rights reserved.&nbsp;<br /> You are receiving this email because you previously signed up for information from the Masters.<br />If you no longer wish to receive newsletter emails from us,&nbsp;<span><a href="#">unsubscribe</a></span> here.</mj-text></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#1C4932"><mj-column><mj-divider border-width="1px" border-color="#FFFFFF" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px"></mj-divider></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="10px" padding-right="10px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="10px" background-color="#1C4932"><mj-column><mj-text align="center" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Benton Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif" font-size="12px" line-height="22px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px">Augusta National Golf Club, 2604 Washington Rd, Augusta, GA 30904</mj-text></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="10px" padding-right="10px" padding-left="10px" background-color="#1C4932"><mj-column><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/qq7uw68x_1540518_partner_2026_all_040426.gif" alt="Official Partners" width="249px"></mj-image></mj-column></mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>